      <title></title>
      <link href="/2026/02/26/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81/"/>
      <url>/2026/02/26/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="网站源码"><a href="#网站源码" class="headerlink" title="网站源码:"></a>网站源码:</h1><blockquote><p>当开发人员在线上环境中对源代码进行了备份操作，并且将备份文件放在了 web 目录下，就会引起网站源码泄露。</p></blockquote><p><img src="/assets/1.png"></p><h2 id="Way1：手工"><a href="#Way1：手工" class="headerlink" title="Way1：手工"></a>Way1：手工</h2><h2 id="Way2：dirsearch"><a href="#Way2：dirsearch" class="headerlink" title="Way2：dirsearch"></a>Way2：dirsearch</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dirsearch -u http://&lt;题目地址&gt;/ -e tar,tar.gz,zip,rar  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><code>pip3 install dirsearch</code></p><p><code>-e</code> &#x3D; <strong><code>--extensions</code></strong> ，文件扩展名</p></blockquote><p><img src="/assets/2.png"></p><h2 id="Way3-Burp-Suite-lntruder"><a href="#Way3-Burp-Suite-lntruder" class="headerlink" title="Way3:Burp Suite lntruder"></a>Way3:Burp Suite lntruder</h2><p><strong>右键 → Send to Intruder</strong></p><p>切换到 <strong>Intruder</strong> 标签页</p><ul><li><p><strong>Positions</strong> 页：</p><p>先点 <strong>Clear §</strong> 把所有标记清掉</p><p>把请求改成这样：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">GET /§name§.§ext§ HTTP/1.1</span><br><span class="line">Host: challenge-fd69b1bf161f7bae.sandbox.ctfhub.com:10800</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Attack type</strong> 改成 <strong>Cluster bomb attack</strong>（两个 payload 组合用）</p></li></ul><p>切换到 <strong>Payloads</strong> 页</p><ul><li><p>Payload set 1：</p><p>Payload type: <strong>Simple list</strong></p><p>点击 <strong>Load</strong>，新建一个 <code>names.txt</code>  内容：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">web</span><br><span class="line">website</span><br><span class="line">backup</span><br><span class="line">back</span><br><span class="line">www</span><br><span class="line">wwwroot</span><br><span class="line">temp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/assets/3.png"></p></li><li><p>Payload set 2：</p><p>Payload type: <strong>Simple list</strong></p><p>新建 <code>exts.txt</code>  内容：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">zip</span><br><span class="line">tar</span><br><span class="line">tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">rar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p><strong>Start attack</strong></p><p><img src="/assets/4.png"></p><p><strong>下载  <a href="http://www.zip/">www.zip</a></strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -o www.zip http://&lt;题目地址&gt;/www.zip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>curl访问获取 flag:</strong></p><p><img src="/assets/5.png"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
