      <title></title>
      <link href="/2026/02/26/302%E8%B7%B3%E8%BD%AC/302%E8%B7%B3%E8%BD%AC/"/>
      <url>/2026/02/26/302%E8%B7%B3%E8%BD%AC/302%E8%B7%B3%E8%BD%AC/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="CTFHub-Web-—-302-跳转"><a href="#CTFHub-Web-—-302-跳转" class="headerlink" title="CTFHub Web — 302 跳转"></a>CTFHub Web — 302 跳转</h1><h2 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h2><p>打开页面，显示 “No Flag here!”，有一个 “Give me Flag” 的链接，点进去会跳转到 <code>index.html</code>，flag 没了。</p><p><img src="/assets/01_challenge_page.png" alt="题目页面"></p><p>问题就在这个跳转上，服务器返回的是 302，flag 藏在 302 响应包里，浏览器自动跟着跳走了，所以看不到。</p><hr><h2 id="解法"><a href="#解法" class="headerlink" title="解法"></a>解法</h2><h3 id="Burp-Suite"><a href="#Burp-Suite" class="headerlink" title="Burp Suite"></a>Burp Suite</h3><p>用 Burp 拦截请求，点 “Give me Flag” 的时候抓包，直接在响应里就能看到 flag，不用跟着跳。</p><p><img src="/assets/02_burpsuite_302_flag.png" alt="Burp Suite 抓到 302 响应中的 flag"></p><h3 id="curl"><a href="#curl" class="headerlink" title="curl"></a>curl</h3><p>curl 默认不跟随跳转，直接请求 <code>index.php</code> 就能拿到 flag：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl http://challenge-xxx.ctfhub.com:10800/index.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/assets/03_curl_flag.png" alt="curl 获取 flag"></p><h3 id="Python-requests"><a href="#Python-requests" class="headerlink" title="Python requests"></a>Python requests</h3><p><code>requests</code> 默认会跟随跳转，加上 <code>allow_redirects=False</code> 就能停在 302 那一层拿到 flag：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">r = requests.get(<span class="string">&quot;http://challenge-xxx.ctfhub.com:10800/index.php&quot;</span>, allow_redirects=<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(r.text)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/assets/04_python_requests_flag.png" alt="Python requests 获取 flag"></p><h3 id="HTTPie"><a href="#HTTPie" class="headerlink" title="HTTPie"></a>HTTPie</h3><p>HTTPie 默认不跟随跳转，直接请求就行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http http://challenge-da252dc83e5efc49.sandbox.ctfhub.com:10800/index.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/assets/05_httpie_flag.png" alt="HTTPie 获取 flag"></p><blockquote><p>302 这种细节很容易被忽略，但往往 flag 就藏在那一跳里。以后遇到跳转，先别急着跟，停下来看看响应包，说不定惊喜就在里面。</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
